  "commit_message": "new_installer: use existing global state marshaler with performance opt (#52470)\n\n`new_installer.GlobalState` was a verbatim copy of\n`subprocess_context.GlobalStateMarshaler`, minus the environment\nhandling. It's purpose was to drop the environment from the marshaler\nfor performance reasons where it's not necessary.\n\n`subprocess_context.GlobalStateMarshaler` already has a constructor\nargument to avoid serializing the environment.\n\nThis PR changes the new installer to use\n`subprocess_context.Glob",
